<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>For My Best Friend ❤️</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }body {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4);
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh;
        text-align: center;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .container {
        background: white;
        padding: 40px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        max-width: 400px;
        animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        color: #ff4d6d;
    }

    p {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #444;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    button {
        background: #ff4d6d;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        border-radius: 25px;
        font-size: 16px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: 0.3s ease;
    }

    button:hover {
        background: #e63956;
        transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .hidden-message {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #ff4d6d;
        display: none;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
        from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
        to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .hearts {
        position: absolute;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        overflow: hidden;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        z-index: -1;
    }

    .heart {
        position: absolute;
        color: #ff4d6d;
        animation: float 6s linear infinite;
        font-size: 20px;
    }

    @keyframes float {
        0% { transform: translateY(100vh); opacity: 1; }
        100% { transform: translateY(-10vh); opacity: 0; }
    }
</style>

</head>
<body><div class="hearts" id="hearts"></div><div class="container">
    <h1>Hey Shaheena 💖</h1>
    <p>You are one of the most amazing people in my life. And yes… even when we say “fuck you bitch” to each other, it’s pure friendship energy 😂 This little website is just to remind you how special you are to me.</p>
    <button onclick="showMessage()">Click for a Surprise 🎁</button>
    <div class="hidden-message" id="message">
        No matter what happens, I’ll always be there for you. From roasting each other with “fuck you bitch” to supporting each other in real life — you’re my forever best friend. 💕
    </div>
</div><script>
    function showMessage() {
        document.getElementById("message").style.display = "block";
    }

    function createHeart() {
        const heart = document.createElement('div');
        heart.classList.add('heart');
        heart.innerHTML = '❤';
        heart.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + 'vw';
        heart.style.animationDuration = (Math.random() * 3 + 3) + 's';
        document.getElementById('hearts').appendChild(heart);
        setTimeout(() => heart.remove(), 6000);
    }

    setInterval(createHeart, 500);
</script></body>
</html>
